# API Overview Sites
This contains a non-exhaustive list of API overview sites, which explain briefly how the API works and how developers can hook into the API.

Of course, implementations vary, but the basic MineQuest structure remains.
If you don't know what the MineQuest structure is, please see [our website](http://www.theminequest.com/) before proceeding further.

* [MineQuest-API](http://minequest.github.com/MineQuest-API/)
